                                <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://accidentsolution.ca/video-capsules/compensation-for-loss-of-income/" rel="bookmark">Compensation for loss of income</a></h2>                            </header>
                            <br><p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p>According to section 44 of the Act, compensation for loss of income (also known as CLI) is paid to workers who suffer from a work-related accident, an occupational disease, a relapse, or a worsening injury which prevents them from carrying out their duties.  ..</p><br><br><p class="link-more"><a href="https://accidentsolution.ca/video-capsules/compensation-for-loss-of-income/" class="more-link">Continue reading <span class="screen-reader-text"> "Compensation for loss of income"</span><br/><br/></a></p>
